WEBVTT

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:22.480
Anda tuhan dan buddha tanah liat dan kayu!

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:26.560
Anda telah menikmati persembahan dunia fana,

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:29.320
